We are Triazine Software

Triazine Software is CMMI Level 3, ISO certified technology outsourcing, software development, and consulting company having its development center in Delhi-NCR (India) region with international footprints in Africa, Australia, US, UK, UAE.

As one of the leading IT service organizations, we are focused on building an innovative future, one that is driven by quality software solutions for mobile and desktop.

Our team of experts have wide experience, working with customers from myriad industries, incorporating the most updated technology trends to offer you the most innovative solutions.

Our Culture

Our company culture is characterized by a supportive and inclusive work environment where everyone is encouraged to share their ideas and opinions. We value diversity, equity, and inclusion, and we believe that a diverse team leads to better decision-making and innovation.

We strive to create a work environment that is both challenging and supportive. We provide our employees with the tools and resources they need to succeed, as well as opportunities for professional development and growth. We also offer a range of benefits and perks designed to support our employees' physical, mental, and emotional wellbeing.

Our History

Ever since laying our foundation in 2015 with a small group of people and an even smaller clientele, in all these years, we've had the privilege to work with several companies located around the globe, including North America, Europe, Middle East, Africa, and Asia, assisted 150+ organizations in varied industrial genres, and delivered impeccable end-to-end product engineering, digital transformation, and business transformation solutions.

Today, we’re an industry-recognized company of 150+ skilled consultants and delivered more than 300+ projects.

Our Accolades, Partnerships & Certifications
Through all the years, we’ve been appraised and praised for our high industry standards.

Our Software Development Process

We examine, envision, and execute your software development requirements. Our certified experts offer maintenance and support post-product designing and development. We ensure that your business IT solutions are competitive enough and help you stay ahead of the incumbents in the industry.

this is how we work

  • Strategy
  • Plan
  • Design
  • Development
  • Test
  • Launch

    • Strategy

    Our team work closely with the customer todiscuss their Mission, Vision, Goals, Target Markets etc. in detailto get a good understanding of customer’s business and priorities. Based on the discussion, the team prepares an approach document about the process which is going to be followed to achieve the outlined goals and objectives.


    Plan

    Once the strategy is in place, the team prepares a working plan, breaking down the strategy into actionable items with timelines and milestones and shares it with all stakeholders to ensure that everyone is aligned.


    Design

    Planning is followed by creation ofWireframes & Design Concepts. A wireframe is a simple visual representation of various sections which is designed considering various user experience principles and design conventions. After discussion with the customers the wireframes go through iterations as required to make the final product meet business expectations as closely as possible


    Development

    We useHTML for creating web/mobile pages and CSS stylesheets for styling. All the development is done in an Agile way.Agile methodology helps increase productivity and accommodates changes at any stage of the cycle without taking much time.


    Test

    Testing is the most important step in the whole processthat decides success or failure of the product. The team takes feedback from users and makes changes in the product to improve user experience and work towards delighting them


    Launch

    This is the final leg of the process, where after all the feedbacks/suggestions, testing, the final product is deployed taking care of software& hardware requirements with the customer which is followed by support to users on any issues they might feel and guiding them on the usage.
